    <div class="Vcard_img">
      <img width="700" height="394" src="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19-05-19_ein_europa_demo_foto_mirko_lux_print_727.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Ein Europa für Alle demonstration. Berlin, May 2019. | ©Mirko Lux" srcset="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19-05-19_ein_europa_demo_foto_mirko_lux_print_727.jpg 700w, https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19-05-19_ein_europa_demo_foto_mirko_lux_print_727-300x169.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" />      <div class="Vcard_tags">
        <a href="https://voxeurop.eu/es/typology/interview-es/"><span style="background-color: #1e32bb;" class="category_tag">Entrevista</span></a>                  <a href="javascript:void(0);"><span
              class="sub_category_tag $custom_classes strap_line">INICIATIVA CITIZENS TAKE OVER EUROPE:</span></a>
              </div>
    </div>
    <div class="single-header__title text-center text-sm-left">
      <h1>Queremos una Europa protectora y protegida”</h1>
      <p>El 9 de mayo, día de Europa, la alianza “Citizens Take Over Europe” (los ciudadanos toman Europa) inaugura su asamblea, un espacio de diálogo entre ciudadanos sobre el futuro de Europa. Esta asamblea es necesaria porque en la Conferencia sobre el Futuro de Europa, organizada por la Unión Europea, se ha relegado a un segundo plano a la sociedad civil, explican Marta Cillero, Michele Fiorillo y Martin Pairet.</p>
      <div class="d-bloc my-2 publish_date_time">Publicado en 13 mayo 2020 a las 10:56</div>    </div>
    <div class="single-header__author">
      <ul>
                  <li><a href="https://voxeurop.eu/es/author/catherine-andrevoxeurop-eu/" title="Entradas por Catherine André" class="author url fn" rel="author">Catherine André</a>                      </li>
                              </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="single-article__language single-article__language__mobile">
      <ul> <li><a class='es wpml-ls-link'  href='javascript:void(0)'>es </a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link fr" href="https://voxeurop.eu/fr/we-want-a-europe-that-cares-and-is-taken-care-of/">fr</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link en" href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/we-want-a-europe-that-cares-and-is-taken-care-of/">en</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link de" href="https://voxeurop.eu/de/we-want-a-europe-that-cares-and-is-taken-care-of/">de</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link it" href="https://voxeurop.eu/it/we-want-a-europe-that-cares-and-is-taken-care-of/">it</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pl" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pl/we-want-a-europe-that-cares-and-is-taken-care-of/">pl</a></li></ul>      <div class="mobile-language-separator"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="single-header__image">
              <div class="single-header__image__container">
          <img width="700" height="394" src="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19-05-19_ein_europa_demo_foto_mirko_lux_print_727.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Ein Europa für Alle demonstration. Berlin, May 2019. | ©Mirko Lux" srcset="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19-05-19_ein_europa_demo_foto_mirko_lux_print_727.jpg 700w, https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19-05-19_ein_europa_demo_foto_mirko_lux_print_727-300x169.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" />                  </div>
